data.description:
319 Coral Dr, Fort Walton Beach, FL 32548 is a single family home that contains 1,567 sq ft and was built in 1960. It contains 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. This home last sold for $274,900 in March 2021. 
 
The Zestimate for this house is $333,000. The Rent Zestimate for this home is $2,194/mo.
